txt.en: Shades haunt the empty carcass of a long-abandoned house, posing a threat to those who draw too near the forgotten structure. If combat will lay these spirits to rest, it falls to you to make the attempt.

TBD Several shades reside near this house, that has long been abandoned.  Lay these poor spirits to rest where you find them.

You do not know if your efforts here will last, but for now you have given rest to some of the shades haunting this abandoned house in the Floodfells. Those spirits that remain will serve as a reminder and a warning to those who dare draw near: not all houses that seem empty are truly so....
